body_html:
Some more data:

I tried repro'ing this issue with the given events file.
Building tensorflow from scratch, tensorboard was working as expected.
Doing a pip install on my Ubuntu 14.04 machine, tf 0.7.1, I was able to see the issue (no graphs showing up in tensorboard).
When I pip uninstalled and reinstalled tensorflow, tensorboard started working as expected.
